text.tspan: Pitch: Postmates for math tutors. Imagine studying for a
math exam and you’re stumped on a problem. How will you
solve this type of problem when you encounter it on the
exam? With Accomplish’s mobile app, you can request a
math tutor to come to you on demand and explain it to you
In sophomore year of college, I designed the app and
website interface for math tutoring startup Accomplish. Still
new to the world of UI, I spent much of my time reading
case studies and learning best practices. My goals at the
time were: ease of use, simplicity, and brand consistency.
Which looking back should be a given regardless of
organization principles, but I like returning to this project
every now and then to see what I would do differently today.
